  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After accumulating an insurmountable amount of debt, you are compelled to accept a cryptic invitation to partake in a high-stakes gambling endeavor. You have the option to ascend the ranks of the poker table or employ alternative methods to settle your financial obligations while gradually unraveling the enigmatic secrets surrounding this game. It is imperative that you proceed with utmost caution as not everyone can endure the consequences of failure.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple but not Simplistic</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a series of elaborate games, win chips to offset your debts, and leave your cage to regain your freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/6501360e537f817a77393b3f96d9c4f4.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/6501360e537f817a77393b3f96d9c4f4.avif?t=1737084540 width=1170 height=658 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several new sets of rules for card games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhanced psychological gaming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive experience</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Microeconomic Systems</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your assets, buy props to give you an edge at the tables, or take the plunge into bigger bets - stocks and horse betting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/122da84787d7fd9af4cc0080b408f606.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/122da84787d7fd9af4cc0080b408f606.avif?t=1737084540 width=1170 height=658 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/e51755d4d5fbe30c86991db79a10105e.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/e51755d4d5fbe30c86991db79a10105e.avif?t=1737084540 width=1170 height=658 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/53c5b29afe5d85510b248c4155168226.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/53c5b29afe5d85510b248c4155168226.avif?t=1737084540 width=1170 height=658 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Markets with dynamic changes in commodity prices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stocks associated with market volatility</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tigger machine and racecourses</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discovering the Truth of the Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Empty your debt and get out, or explore the cage and learn the dark secrets behind the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/ec30e3df40850fd251613d9f19ccc90f.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/ec30e3df40850fd251613d9f19ccc90f.avif?t=1737084540 width=1170 height=658 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with Your Friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create online poker games, choose your style of play, and have fun with your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
